{"metadata":{"title":"activateAction(actionName:parameter:)","extendedModule":"GIO","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO19ActionGroupProtocolPAAE08activateB010actionName9parameterySPys4Int8VGSg_4GLib10VariantRefVSgtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO11ApplicationC","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"activateAction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"actionName"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"parameter","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application\/activateAction(actionName:parameter:)"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"activateAction","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"actionName"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"parameter"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the action is expecting a parameter, then the correct type of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"parameter must be given as "},{"code":"parameter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":".  If the action is expecting no"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parameters then "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"parameter"},{"text":" must be ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"type":"text","text":".  See"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.ActionGroup.get_action_parameter_type","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the [type"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup"},{"text":"] implementation supports asynchronous remote","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"activation over D-Bus, this call may return before the relevant"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"D-Bus traffic has been sent, or any replies have been received. In","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order to block on such asynchronous activation calls,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.DBusConnection.flush"},{"type":"text","text":"] should be called prior to the code, which"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"depends on the result of the action activation. Without flushing","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the D-Bus connection, there is no guarantee that the action would"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"have been activated."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code which runs in a remote app instance, shows an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"example of a ‘quit’ action being activated on the primary app","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"instance over D-Bus. Here [method"},{"code":"Gio.DBusConnection.flush","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] is called","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"before "},{"code":"exit()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Without "},{"code":"g_dbus_connection_flush()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the ‘quit’ action"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"may fail to be activated on the primary instance.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ call ‘quit’ action on primary instance","g_action_group_activate_action (G_ACTION_GROUP (app), \"quit\", NULL);","","\/\/ make sure the action is activated now","g_dbus_connection_flush (…);","","g_debug (\"Application has been terminated. Exiting.\");","","exit (0);"],"syntax":"c","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application\/ActionGroupProtocol-Implementations"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Activate the named action within ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"actionGroup"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/application\/activateaction(actionname:parameter:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/Application/activateAction(actionName:parameter:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application\/activateAction(actionName:parameter:)","title":"activateAction(actionName:parameter:)","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Activate the named action within "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"actionGroup"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"activateAction","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"actionName"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":